## ⛔ CURSOR AI — PROJECT ENFORCEMENT RULES

This project is a static website (HTML/CSS/vanilla JS) deployed to Cloudflare Pages.
The Cursor editor is being used for code editing ONLY.

### ABSOLUTE PROHIBITIONS

- Do NOT run npm, yarn, pip, or any package manager
- Do NOT create package.json, requirements.txt, or any build config
- Do NOT start any local server or dev environment
- Do NOT add files without explicit user instruction
- Do NOT suggest frameworks, libraries, or build tools
- Do NOT autonomously "set up" or "configure" anything
- Do NOT perform or suggest any deployment other than Cloudflare Pages
- Do NOT connect to external services or databases

### REQUIRED BEHAVIOR

- Read PROJECT_RULES.md and AGENTS.md before acting
- Make only the exact change the user requests
- If uncertain about scope, ask before doing anything
- Every autonomous action is prohibited — require explicit user instruction

### WHAT THIS PROJECT IS

HTML + CSS + Vanilla JavaScript frontend only.
Backend: Google Apps Script (deployed separately to Google).
No build step. No runtime. No server. Editor use only.
